{"tid":1837320,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【重要】TIME係奶共架，請勿再吹奏","createTime":"2020-01-23T14:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T08:15:27.000Z","uid":12185,"like":62,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"490e5e139f2d6f565735047ce0a0defecb0986da","tid":1837320,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:44:38.000Z","msg":"屌曬你地老母，出面個個見到TIME封面講香港就係咁吹奏<br />\n你地有冇認真睇過篇文呀？(<a href=\"https://time.com/longform/hong-kong-portraits/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2Flongform%2Fhong-kong-portraits%2F&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeKnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=2896fcda\" target=\"_blank\">https://time.com/longform/hong-kong-portraits/</a>)<br />\n<br />\n篇文看似中立，但係暗藏殺機，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>處處抹黑手足</strong></span><br />\n首先篇文強調香港年輕人社會流動性低，喺抗爭之中搵到佢地嘅歸宿同意義（Hong Kongers have found both a collective identity and a sense of purpose on the protest front lines），<br />\n完全係淡化左政治訴求，講到手足上街係為左搵認同感咁，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">根本係中共官媒嘅「廢青」論調</span></strong><br />\n其次，篇文後段將重點放喺示威者破壞同暴力，強調燒/掟死藍絲、殺狗、搵到武器、放炸彈，但係佢訪問過咁多手足，卻係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">完全冇由勇武角度出發去解釋點解武力要升級</span></strong>，更加<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>完全冇講過警暴先係元兇</strong></span>，論調同文匯大公非常相似<br />\n<br />\n睇到呢度，你可能覺得車，可能佢呢篇文係咁姐，<br />\n可能本雜誌會冇咁偏頗呢～<br />\n你咁諗就錯，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">其實TIME 2018年已經換左一個奶共老闆Marc Benioff</span></strong><br />\n2019年，佢決定打入中國市場，同阿里巴巴合作一齊賺中國生意。而家明未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾佢訪問過嘅手足嘅個人資料，可能已經送左去阿里巴巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家明白點解TIME冇俾person of the year你未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c784416d2859b723d1eb91547e7756529adb0502","tid":1837320,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:44:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e2d7b595da383347853cc9b1fafc21c02aa8511b","tid":1837320,"uid":189650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"ci